The paper focuses on the task of generating short summaries of commits, which is a software engineering task. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves natural language processing techniques, such as verb and object generation, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions using a classifier, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
